# -*- mode: Org; -*-

* General concept
  Simple text-based multiplayer shooter.
  Client-server mechanism based on binary protocol.
  
* Closer details
** Server

   players list -+-> player 1 -> recieve data and insert into messages queue
   (slots)       +-> player 2 <-.                    |
                 +-> ...        |                    |
                 '-> player n   |                    |
                                |            ________V_______
   world -> messages queue manager <------- ( messages queue )
            Fetch messages then update       ----------------
            world and send them to players. 

** Client

   First thread draw the user interface.
   Second recieves data and send signal to the first.
            
